    "According to the study, combining traditional machine learning methods with deep learning may accurately classify cervical cancer.",
    "Using the UCI cervical cancer risk factor dataset, Alsmariy et al.",
    "in [26] developed a machine-learning algorithm to predict cervical cancer.",
    "They used PCA (principal component analysis) in conjunction with SMOTE (synthetic minority oversampling approach) to address the problem of class imbalance.",
